{"type": "article", "id": 18490, "title": "花瓣吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-04T07:40:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 54, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004024yze1u2bC0pa4nDj6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t荷兰设计工作室 Bertjan Pot 曾为家具品牌 Moooi 设计了吊灯 Heracleum，在一个主框架下延伸出小的分支，上面点缀着圆片形的灯泡，就像从一棵树里长出来的。这组 Heracleum Endless 是一个扩大版，将吊灯沿着流动的线条展开，几十个灯泡散着打开，有黄铜和金属镍两种支架，最长可达 10 米，很适合酒店大堂或展会，<a href=\"http://www.moooi.com/products/heracleum-endless\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004022vDHlAZzUKugSs5hO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004022bzsDWvL6EC3Uf8ru.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004023Bzwms8CgY2xKdcAF.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004023mvt6IEdiZ2PxyGJF.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}